            <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:1;25:16" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/kheat/Documents/GitHub/New%20folder/LearningDITA/en-us/Learning_and_training_specialization/topics/where_do_you_use_the_l_t_specialization_.dita">Here are just a few use cases for where you might use the DITA Learning &amp;
